# Hawking Photon Emission Model
# COMAF × PNMS Addendum: CHARGE + POWER blocks
# Physical scenario: evaporating black hole emitting Hawking radiation.
# Modeled as a CHARGE + POWER system at Planck scale.
# Paper reference: §6.5 Black Hole Entropy, §8 Demo Cases (TC4/TC5 family)
# Status: syntax demo + addendum coverage
ENTITY: HawkingEmitter
CYCLE: CPL-7
FRAME: t ∈ [0, 1 WarpTick]
UNITS: Planck

ENTROPY S:
  evolve Boltzmann {
    init: 1.05e77
    max: 1.05e78
    scale: 1e20 Plaseconds
  }

STABILITY:
  metric D = exp(-|∇S| · t)

CHARGE q_eff: alpha * e_p

POWER P_hawking: hbar * c^6 / (M * M)

IF D(t) < 0.01:
  emit {
    energy: E_hawking
    decay: 1.0
  }

ON cycle.end:
  S = S / (1 + alpha)
